        <num>CC 876</num>
        <heading>876.  Kinds of successors</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 876.  Kinds of successors
There are two kinds of successors corresponding to the two kinds of
succession described in the preceding articles:
Testate successors, also called legatees.
Intestate successors, also called heirs.</p>
        </content>
